## Colours for items in the index
color index color207 color233 ~N
color index color208 color233 ~O
color index brightyellow color233 ~F
color index color233 color42 ~T
color index brightred color233 ~D
mono index bold ~N
mono index bold ~F
mono index bold ~T
mono index bold ~D

color status    white color233
color indicator white color233
color search    white color233
color markers   white color233

## Highlights inside the body of a message.

## URLs
color body brightgreen color233 "(http|https|ftp|news|telnet|finger)://[^ \"\t\r\n]*"
color body brightgreen color233 "mailto:[-a-z_0-9.]+@[-a-z_0-9.]+"
mono body bold "(http|ftp|news|telnet|finger)://[^ \"\t\r\n]*"
mono body bold "mailto:[-a-z_0-9.]+@[-a-z_0-9.]+"

## Email addresses.
color body brightgreen color233 "[-a-z_0-9.%$]+@[-a-z_0-9.]+\\.[-a-z][-a-z]+"

## pgp
color body      blue  default "^(gpg: )?Good signature"
color body      brightgreen  default "^(gpg: )?encrypted"
color body      brightred    default "^(gpg: )?Bad signature"
color body      red          default "^(gpg: )?warning:"
color body      red          default "^(gpg: ).*failed:"

